<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id602f32ac-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s1021"><num value="1021">§ 1021.</num><heading> Federal exemption from State water laws</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Nothing in this chapter shall constitute an express or implied claim or denial on the part of the Federal Government as to its exemption from State water laws.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id602f32ad-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58">(<ref href="/us/pl/91/581/s22">Pub. L. 91–581, § 22</ref>, <date date="1970-12-24">Dec. 24, 1970</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/84/1573">84 Stat. 1573</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/109/58/tII/s236/20">Pub. L. 109–58, title II, § 236(20)</ref>, <date date="2005-08-08">Aug. 8, 2005</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/119/673">119 Stat. 673</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
